The drug '''''pentabenzedralyne''''' was created during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], designed to heighten the aggression of combatants. Years later, after the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]], the [[Camarina Connection]] gang renewed production of pentabenzedralyne on a massive scale aboard the factory ship ''[[Black Lotus]]'', as part of a scheme to destabilize [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]&mdash;and make themselves rich in the process.

==Behind the scenes==
The only mention of pentabenzedralyne occurs in the French roleplaying-game magazine ''[[Casus Belli 89]]''.

